{"lemma":"قَرْعُ","slug":"قَرْعُ","root":"ق.ر.ع","root_slug":"ق-ر-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ر-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":9,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":20},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n42605","n42611"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to knock, rap, strike; to cudgel, to driveback with a stick","tags":["ambitransitive","transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to knock, rap, strike; to beat the drum, to ring, to clink","tags":["ambitransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to reproach, to impugn the character of","tags":["ambitransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cover (a mare) (of a stallion)","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cast lots","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be the winner in casting lots","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to ring, to jingle","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to creak, to crunch","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to creak, to crunch; to itch, to cause remorse","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to accept advice"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to conquer in throwing the javelin or spear"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be empty, deserted, bare","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be empty, deserted, bare; to be bald","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cuss, to reprimand","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to percuss, to ring, to drum","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of قَرَعَ (qaraʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of قَرِعَ (qariʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"button, pustule, itch, rash","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"لحب القرع والديدان الكبير\nسرخس وبرنج وقنبيل وتربذ وترمس ومر متساوية الشربة أربعة دراهم بماء حار","english":"For (the treatment of ) flukes and large worms\nMale fern, embelia, kamala, turpeth, lupine, and myrrh (in) equal (parts). A potion (may be made by using) four dirham (of it) with hot water."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pumpkin, gourd","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"chemical retort","tags":["archaic","collective"],"examples":[{"text":"القَرْع، والأَنْبِيق، وهما آلتا صُنَّاع ماء الوَرْد. والسفلى هي القرع، والعليا على هيئة المِحْجمة، هي الأنبيق.","english":"The retort and the still are two implements of those who make rose-water. The lower is the retort, the upper of the shape of a cupping glass, that is the still."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From ق ر ع (q r ʕ), ranging in semantics from casting lots and sortition with sticks or arrow-shafts to casting the whip and otherwise preceding rough.\n\nFrom Classical Syriac ܩܪܐܐ (qarrʾā)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n42605","headword_ar":"قَرَعَ","root":"qrE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqoraEN","text_ar":"مَقْرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for an inf. n. (Mgh, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gmz","text_ar":"غمز"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraEa fiY miqoraEihi","text_ar":"قَرَعَ فِى مِقْرَعِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba fiY miDorbihi","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ فِى مِضْربِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Drb","text_ar":"ضرب"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraEa SafaAtahu","text_ar":"قَرَعَ صَفَاتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He impugned his character; blamed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"censured him; spoke against him"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gmz","text_ar":"غمز"},{"kind":"text","text":".) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magomazN","text_ar":"مَغْمَزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraEa bayona Zufori","text_ar":"قَرَعَ بَيْنَ ظُفْرِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibohaAmihi waZufori sab~aAbatihi","text_ar":"اـِبْهَامِهِ وَظُفْرِ سَبَّابَتِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fillipped with the nail of his thumb and that of his forefinger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, K, * TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"znjr","text_ar":"زنجر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa AlfaHolu laA yuqoraEu A^anofuhu","text_ar":"هُوَ الفَحْلُ لَا يُقْرَعُ اَنْفُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anofN","text_ar":"اَنْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qdE","text_ar":"قدع"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraEa A^anofahu","text_ar":"قَرَعَ اَنْفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroEN","text_ar":"قَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He rejected him, repelled him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"turned him back;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely a suitor in a case of marriage. (TA, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bDE","text_ar":"بضع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buDoEN","text_ar":"بُضْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a AlEaSaA quriEato li*iY AlHilomi","text_ar":"اـِنَّ العَصَا قُرِعَتْ لِذِى الحِلْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see Freytag's Arab. Prov. i. 55; and Har, 656. ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yuqoraEu lahu AlEaSaA","text_ar":"لَا يُقْرَعُ لَهُ العَصَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": see Freytag's Arab. Prov. ii. 543, and Har, 655, in two places. ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraEahu biEaSaA AlmalaAmapi","text_ar":"قَرَعَهُ بِعَصَا المَلَامَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSFA","text_ar":"عَصًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraEotu raA^osahu biAlEaSaA","text_ar":"قَرَعْتُ رَاْسَهُ بِالعَصَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAls~ayofi","text_ar":"بِالسَّيْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraEotu","text_ar":"فَرَعْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraEa Zunobuwba baEiyrihi","text_ar":"قَرَعَ ظُنْبُوبَ بَعِيرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraEa liA^amorihi Zunobuwbahu","text_ar":"قَرَعَ لِاَمْرِهِ ظُنْبُوبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": &c.: see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Znb","text_ar":"ظنب"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraEa liloA^amori saAqahu","text_ar":"قَرَعَ لِلْاَمْرِ سَاقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAqN","text_ar":"سَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n42611","headword_ar":"قَرَعٌ","root":"qrE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Bare pieces of ground amid herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xfY","text_ar":"خفى"},{"kind":"text","text":", from a trad.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}